# ğŸš€ GUNSHOT SUMMARY

âœ… Use **partitioning for huge tables**
âœ… Use **RANGE(created\_at)** for transactions
âœ… Always include partition key in `PRIMARY KEY`
âœ… Use `EXPLAIN` to verify pruning
âœ… Add/drop partitions yearly or monthly

